            verbs: ["Identify", "Determine", "Deduce", "Classify", "Analyse", "Interpret", "Distinguish"],
            whatDistinguishesThisLevel: "Analyze requires evidence-to-conclusion reasoning. 'Given species composition data from four plots at a chronosequence site, rank the plots by estimated succession stage and justify your ranking' requires the student to read the evidence and infer the order — the answer is not given.",
